summary:
My carrier in the Netherlands  start in the Mc’donalds as a cashier because my language skills was very low in the beginning.
Later I started working in the hotel industry  as Housekeeping and  then lately I’ve been Floor Supervisor - Working, leading and managed people at work .
During the corona time I was working in Data center as assistant and as helping in the office.
I have also good creative skill as a Photographer working with Photoshop program . Working now as a Host at Airbnb .

I have experience as a photographer (8 years) 
I have also experience as bartender is more than 10 years.
I have experience as Houskeeping floor supervisor 2 years.
I have experience as Call center specialist 1 year (Slovakia) 
I have experience as Customer support specialist 1year (Slovakia)

I consider myself a flexible person who is able to work under stressful conditions.I am a positive thinker.i like working with people. I have no fear of new things and tasks.
I love traveling and exploring new cultures around the world .
Im open mind and calm friendly person.
Creative and artistic  soul  always willing to learn new things.
